</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>中國女子誤吞藍牙耳機入肚，與另一隻耳機感應才找到</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/02/26/earphone-3/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=earphone-3</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[EMMA]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 26 Feb 2022 05:15:00 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1087198</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>近日，河北邯鄲一位女孩在睡覺時誤將一隻藍牙耳機給吞下，其後看醫生竟利用另一隻耳機互相感應才能找出耳機位置。 &#038; [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>近日，河北邯鄲一位女孩在睡覺時誤將一隻藍牙耳機給吞下，其後看醫生竟利用另一隻耳機互相感應才能找出耳機位置。</p><p>據當事人表示，她於 2 月 18 日，晚間戴著藍牙耳機睡覺時，迷迷糊糊中感覺到嘴裡有東西，便直接將它咽了下來去，第二天早上醒來後發現耳機不見。經過回憶及查證後，該女子確定昨晚所吞的東西便是藍牙耳機。她指自己雖然有意識，但因太累了而醒不過來。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/b2cc82ea-9247-11ec-be44-560003748b73.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1087433" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/b2cc82ea-9247-11ec-be44-560003748b73.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="346" /></a></p><p>隨後該女子前往醫院，跟醫生說明情況並於胃部拍攝 X 光照片後亦未能找到該隻藍牙耳機。因此，醫生提議利用將另外一隻耳機貼在肚子上測試能否找到，然而真的感應出耳機已下到大小腸位置在。最後女子決定等待，經過過一夜後，她於 20 號早上將耳機排出。</p><p>不少網友在此事曝光後表示，能順利排出真是萬幸，要是在裡面漏電就糟糕。亦有幽默的網友評論道，「右耳機：左耳機，雖然我無法理解你的經歷，但是你可以不要一直告訴我最後的經歷嗎？」</p><p class="p1"><span class="s1">資料</span><span class="s2">來源、圖片來源：<a href="https://www.airvers.com/the-girl-accidentally-swallowed-the-earphone-while-sleeping-while-listening-to-the-song-the-other-one-can-be-sensed-on-the-stomach/">airvers</a></span></p><p class="p2">—</p><p class="p2"><span class="s3">unwire.hk</span> Mewe <span class="s4">專頁：</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span class="s3">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=lqRgpsa1Yew:QXHBXhXLD3E:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=lqRgpsa1Yew:QXHBXhXLD3E:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>全新 Subaru BRZ 登陸香港，第二代純日本跑車最大馬力 234PS</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/02/26/subaru-brz/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=subaru-brz</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 26 Feb 2022 05:10:41 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[車壇動向]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1088120</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>全新 Subaru BRZ (Boxer, Rear-wheel drive, Zenith) 承繼著首代 BRZ [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span lang="ZH-TW">全新 </span><span lang="EN-SG">Subaru BRZ (</span><b><u><span lang="EN-SG">B</span></u></b><span lang="EN-SG">oxer, </span><b><u><span lang="EN-SG">R</span></u></b><span lang="EN-SG">ear-wheel drive, </span><b><u><span lang="EN-SG">Z</span></u></b><span lang="EN-SG">enith)</span><span lang="ZH-TW">承繼著首代</span><span lang="EN-SG">BRZ</span><span lang="ZH-TW">的設計理念，</span><span lang="ZH-TW">提供優越駕駛操控，同時充滿駕駛樂趣。今代透過更多動力、更優異性能、更運動化操控表現、更矚目凌厲的外型設計，作出更極致的進化。另於</span><span lang="EN-SG">6</span><span lang="ZH-TW">前速自動波箱版本中首次加入</span><span lang="EN-SG">Subaru EyeSight</span><span lang="ZH-TW">駕駛輔助系統，全面提升安全性能。</span></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/image003.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1088123" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/image003-694x357.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="357" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/image003-694x357.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/image003-1280x658.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/image003-768x395.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/image003.jpg 1290w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><span lang="ZH-TW">全新</span><span lang="EN-SG">BRZ</span><span lang="ZH-TW">承載經典的前置引擎及後輪驅動跑車佈局，更搭載了更流暢，更強勁動力表現的水平對向</span><span lang="EN-SG"> 4 </span><span lang="ZH-TW">汽缸自然吸氣引擎，於</span><span lang="EN-SG">7,000rpm</span><span lang="ZH-TW">時可釋出</span><span lang="EN-SG">234PS</span><span lang="ZH-TW">最大馬力；及能早於</span><span lang="EN-SG">3,700rpm</span><span lang="ZH-TW">時就拼發出</span><span lang="EN-SG">250Nm</span><span lang="ZH-TW">最大扭力。</span><u></u><u></u><span lang="ZH-TW">除備有</span><span lang="EN-SG">6</span><span lang="ZH-TW">前速手動波箱版本，新一代</span><span lang="EN-SG">6</span><span lang="ZH-TW">前速自動波箱亦比以住更敏銳，改良的</span><span lang="EN-SG">Sport</span><span lang="ZH-TW">模式提供更刺激的加速體驗。電子油門設計亦調較至能於高轉數時能更緊密的配合加速，例如可令駕駛者於出彎時更易於控制動力輸出表現。</span><u></u><u></u></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/image002.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1088122" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/image002-694x314.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="314" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/image002-694x314.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/image002-1280x579.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/image002-768x347.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/image002.jpg 1325w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>今代沿用跑車化雙門設計，車重比上代稍微增加<span lang="EN-SG">10KG</span>，令今代<span lang="EN-HK">BRZ </span>擁有更多動力的水平對向引擎大大改善了動力與重量比例<span lang="EN-SG"> (power-to-weight ratio</span><span lang="EN-HK">)</span>，從而增加了加速時的爽快感。<span lang="EN-SG">6</span>前速手動波箱版本的靜止至<span lang="EN-SG">100km/h</span>的加速只需<span lang="EN-SG">6.3</span>秒，而<span lang="ZH-TW">自動波箱版本則只需</span><span lang="EN-SG">6.9</span><span lang="ZH-TW">秒。</span> <span lang="ZH-TW">除此之外，新一代</span><span lang="EN-SG">BRZ</span><span lang="ZH-TW">各樣操控性能亦有大幅提升，包括由</span><span lang="EN-SG">100km/h</span><span lang="ZH-TW">至完全停止的剎車距離大大縮短，於扭樽測試中表現比上代更敏銳的操控性，於過彎時更少的車身傾側，出彎時亦更有更好的循跡性。</span></p><p><span lang="ZH-TW">車身更長和更低</span><span lang="EN-SG"> (</span><span lang="ZH-TW">分別為</span><span lang="EN-SG">+25 cm</span><span lang="ZH-TW">及</span><span lang="EN-SG"> -10 cm)</span><span lang="ZH-TW">、軸距稍長</span><span lang="EN-SG"> (+5 cm)</span><span lang="ZH-TW">、加闊後輪距</span><span lang="EN-SG"> (+10 cm)</span><span lang="ZH-TW">、更大的輪圈</span><span lang="EN-SG"> (</span><span lang="ZH-TW">從</span><span lang="EN-SG">17</span><span lang="ZH-TW">吋升級到</span><span lang="EN-SG"> 18</span><span lang="ZH-TW">吋</span><span lang="EN-SG">)，令<span lang="ZH-TW">代的車身比例都更顯侵略性及功能性</span></span><span lang="ZH-TW">。用上<span lang="EN-SG">7 </span>吋彩色<span lang="EN-SG"> LCD </span>顯示屏幕為電子速度錶，能以全新方式顯示必要的信息，及各種駕駛模式資訊；駕駛者亦能作個人化調較，以顯示特定數據，例如橫向重力、功率<span lang="EN-SG">/</span>扭力數據，及油耗等。 而<span lang="EN-SG">8</span>吋多媒體顯示屏幕則能提供<span lang="EN-SG">Apple CarPlay </span>資訊娛樂系統、藍牙、語音識別等功能。</span></p><p><strong>Specifications: </strong><strong>全新</strong><strong>Subaru BRZ 2.4</strong><strong>基本資料：</strong></p><table><tbody><tr><td width="150">引擎</td><td width="451">Subaru Boxer® 水平對向 4 汽缸，雙頂凸輪軸 (DOHC)，16 活瓣</td></tr><tr><td width="150">排氣量</td><td width="451">2,387cc</td></tr><tr><td width="150">引擎最大馬力</td><td width="451">234PS/ 7,000rpm</td></tr><tr><td width="150">最大扭力</td><td width="451">250Nm/ 3,700rpm</td></tr><tr><td width="150">極速</td><td width="451">226 km/h (6 前速手動波箱); 216 km/h (6 前速自動波箱)</td></tr><tr><td width="150">尺寸 (長 / 闊 / 高 )</td><td width="451">4,265 mm x 1,775 mm x 1,310 mm</td></tr><tr><td width="150">輪距</td><td width="451">2,575 mm</td></tr><tr><td width="150">離地距</td><td width="451">130mm</td></tr><tr><td width="150">淨重</td><td width="451">1,289kg (6 前速手動波箱); 1,310kg (6 前速自動波箱)</td></tr><tr><td width="150">售價</td><td width="451">HK$399,800 (6 前速手動波箱); HK$423,800 (6 前速自動波箱)</td></tr></tbody></table></p><div class="feedflare">
